title: Google\Cloud\Dlp\V2\Finding
name: Finding
description:
Represents a piece of potentially sensitive content.

Generated from protobuf message google.privacy.dlp.v2.Finding

Extends \Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.quote
params.description: The content that was found. Even if the content is not textual, it may be converted to a textual representation here. Provided if include_quote is true and the finding is less than or equal to 4096 bytes long. If the finding exceeds 4096 bytes in length, the quote may be omitted.

params.name: data.info_type
params.description: The type of content that might have been found. Provided if excluded_types is false.

params.name: data.likelihood
params.description: Confidence of how likely it is that the info_type is correct.

params.name: data.quote_info
params.description: Contains data parsed from quotes. Only populated if include_quote was set to true and a supported infoType was requested. Currently supported infoTypes: DATE, DATE_OF_BIRTH and TIME.
